  <context>
    <background>
      Per r1 ledger entry RB-T050-01 (filed 2026-05-31, fix-by 2026-07-31): the SSE event is consumed by frontend `ChatPane` source-rendering code, which uses defensive `if (event.data.citationId)` checks — so a literal `null` value behaves identically to missing field. The wire-format bloat (~16 bytes per source_pane event without citation) is the only observable effect. The unit test asserts the documented contract (omit when null) and surfaces the gap.

      Same family as RB-T070-02 (task 036, R2SseEventEmitter.CapabilityChangePayload.RetryAfterSeconds). Identical fix pattern.
    </background>
    <dependencies>
      <dependency task="029" status="must-be-complete">Phase 2 exit triple-run validation before Phase 3 starts</dependency>
    </dependencies>
  </context>

  <relevant-files>
    <file>src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/Chat/SseEventTypes/SourcePaneSseEvent.cs</file>
    <file>tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/Services/Ai/Chat/SseEventTypes/ChatSseEventFactoryTests.cs</file>
    <file>projects/sdap-bff.api-test-suite-repair/ledgers/real-bug-ledger.md</file>
  </relevant-files>

  <steps>
    <step order="1">Load r1 ledger entry RB-T050-01 (lines ~182-249) for documented bug + proposed fix.</step>
    <step order="2">Read `src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/Chat/SseEventTypes/SourcePaneSseEvent.cs` focusing on `SourcePaneSseEventData` (~line 48-51).</step>
    <step order="3">Add `[property: JsonIgnore(Condition = JsonIgnoreCondition.WhenWritingNull)]` alongside the existing `[property: JsonPropertyName("citationId")]` on the `CitationId` parameter. Add `using System.Text.Json.Serialization;` if not already imported.</step>
    <step order="4">Build BFF: `dotnet build src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/`. Zero new warnings.</step>
    <step order="5">Edit `tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/Services/Ai/Chat/SseEventTypes/ChatSseEventFactoryTests.cs`: remove `Skip = "..."` on `CreateSourcePaneEvent_WithNullCitationId_OmitsCitationIdField`; remove per-test `[Trait("status","real-bug-pending-fix")]` override.</step>
    <step order="6">Run targeted tests: `dotnet test tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/ --filter "FullyQualifiedName~ChatSseEventFactoryTests"`. Re-enabled test must pass; existing tests must still pass.</step>
    <step order="7">Update ledger row RB-T050-01: status → `repaired`, fix-commit SHA placeholder + today's date.</step>
    <step order="8">Commit: `fix(bff-api): omit null CitationId in SourcePaneSseEventData (RB-T050-01; repaired)` per NFR-04.</step>
    <step order="9">Update `projects/sdap.bff.api-test-suite-repair-r2/current-task.md` with completion + commit SHA.</step>
  </steps>

