    <output type="tests">tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/Services/Ai/Chat/SseEventTypes/ChatSseEventFactoryTests.cs (1 test un-Skip'd)</output>
    <output type="docs">projects/sdap-bff.api-test-suite-repair/ledgers/real-bug-ledger.md (RB-T050-01 row → `repaired`)</output>
